T02TD2736AE:122b-1: a'ary'a ba lo ke te shvar sha ta ksha ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD2736AE:122b-3: 'phags pa 'jig rten dbang phyug yi ge drug pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2736AE:122b-4: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2736AE:122b-5: gang zhig don dam thugs chung snying rje'i dbang gis ye shes skur //
T02TD2736AE:122b-6: gnas mdzad 'gro la bu bzhin mnyam gzigs nas //
T02TD2736AE:122b-7: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho'i 'jigs las sgrol mdzad pa'i //
T02TD2736AE:122b-8: skyob pa'i dbang po 'jig rten mgon la rab btud de//
T02TD2736AE:122b-9: ye nas rnam dag sems nyid ma rig pa'i //
T02TD2736AE:122b-10: glo bur dri mas bsgribs pa'i 'gro la phan don du //
T02TD2736AE:122b-11: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i nang nas theg mchog rdo rje'i lam //
T02TD2736AE:122b-12: sgrib pa myur sel bdud rtsi lta bu bri bar bya //
T02TD2736AE:122b-13: bla ma dkon mchog gsum gus shing ;
T02TD2736AE:122b-14: / snying rje byang chub sems sbyangs te //
T02TD2736AE:122b-15: dbang thob dam tshig ldan pa yi //
T02TD2736AE:122b-16: sgrub la brtson pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD2736AE:122b-17: bkra shis yid 'ong byin chags pa'i //
T02TD2736AE:122b-18: dben pa'i gnas su phyin nas ni //
T02TD2736AE:122b-19: mchod sbyin la sogs sngon song bas //
T02TD2736AE:122b-20: rten dang mchod pa rim bzhin bshams //
T02TD2736AE:122b-21: de nas 'tshe dogs kun spangs nas //
T02TD2736AE:122b-22: khrus byas bde ba'i stan 'dug ste //
T02TD2736AE:122b-23: rang nyid snying gar hr'i: bltas la //
T02TD2736AE:122b-26: bsod nams tshogs ni bsags par bya //
T02TD2736AE:122b-27: 'gro la snying rje chen po dang //
T02TD2736AE:122b-28: byang chub sems kyang bsgom par bya //
T02TD2736AE:122b-29: aom ma h'a sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'a tma konya\ham /
T02TD2736AE:122b-30: dngos rnams thams cad rab sbyangs te //
T02TD2736AE:122b-31: stong pa nyid kyi ngang nyid las //
T02TD2736AE:122b-32: rlung dang bdud rtsi ri rab ste //
T02TD2736AE:122b-33: bh'um las rin chen gzhal yas khang //
T02TD2736AE:122b-34: gru bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD2736AE:122b-35: rta babs la sogs rnam par mdzes //
T02TD2736AE:122b-36: pho brang chu skyes 'dab drug la //
T02TD2736AE:122b-37: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgom //
T02TD2736AE:122b-38: de dbus padma zla ba'i steng //
T02TD2736AE:122b-40: slar 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
T02TD2736AE:122b-41: 'jig rten dbang phyug skur bskyed de //
T02TD2736AE:122b-42: zhal gcig pa la phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD2736AE:122b-43: dang po thugs kar thal mo sbyar //
T02TD2736AE:123a-2: g-yon pa padma dkar po bsnams //
T02TD2736AE:123a-3: sku mdog dung dang kun da 'am //
T02TD2736AE:123a-4: kha ba'i ri ltar dkar ba la //
T02TD2736AE:123a-5: thugs rjes yid tsam dmar ba'i spyan //
T02TD2736AE:123a-6: zhal ni 'dzum pa'i mdangs dang ldan //
T02TD2736AE:123a-7: sku ni mi 'gyur drang po ste //
T02TD2736AE:123a-8: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i skyil krung bzhugs //
T02TD2736AE:123a-9: dbu skra mthon mthing lcang lo 'khyil //
T02TD2736AE:123a-10: aa mi t'a bhas spyi gtsug brgyan //
T02TD2736AE:123a-11: mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang //
T02TD2736AE:123a-12: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cur ldan //
T02TD2736AE:123a-13: rin chen sna tshogs rgyan gyis spras //
T02TD2736AE:123a-14: le brgyan dar gyi na bza' 'chang //
T02TD2736AE:123a-15: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po ni //
T02TD2736AE:123a-16: yum dang sras bcas bskyed par bya //
T02TD2736AE:123a-17: de nas gnas gsum byin brlabs te //
T02TD2736AE:123a-18: spyi bo mgrin pa thugs ka ru //
T02TD2736AE:123a-19: rdo rje gsum mchog snying po 'di //
T02TD2736AE:123a-20: kha dog gsum ldan yi ge dgod //
T02TD2736AE:123a-21: phyogs bcu'i bde gshegs spyan drangs nas //
T02TD2736AE:123a-22: mchod de gsol ba btab pa yis //
T02TD2736AE:123a-23: ye shes bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun gyis //
T02TD2736AE:123a-24: dbang bskur rigs kyi bdag pos brgyan //
T02TD2736AE:123a-25: de nas thugs ka'i sa bon las //
T02TD2736AE:123a-27: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs la //
T02TD2736AE:123a-28: mchod cing gnyis med bsre bar bya //
T02TD2736AE:123a-29: rang sems rnam dag lhar gsal ba //
T02TD2736AE:123a-30: snang ba rang bzhin med pa yi //
T02TD2736AE:123a-31: chu zla me long gzugs brnyan nam //
T02TD2736AE:123a-32: nam mkha' yi ni 'ja' tshon ltar //
T02TD2736AE:123a-33: mtha' gnyis las grol lha yi sku //
T02TD2736AE:123a-34: sku bcas sku ni med pa yi //
T02TD2736AE:123a-35: zung 'jug sgyu ma lta bur ni //
T02TD2736AE:123a-36: rnal 'byor pa yis rtag tu bsgom //
T02TD2736AE:123a-37: de ltar gsal bar gyur pa dang //
T02TD2736AE:123a-38: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad kyis //
T02TD2736AE:123a-39: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gsang sngags 'di //
T02TD2736AE:123a-40: rgyun mi 'chad du bzlas par bya //
T02TD2736AE:123a-42: 'di ni mtshan gyi rgyal po ste /
T02TD2736AE:123a-43: mi mthun dri ma spang byed cing //
T02TD2736AE:123a-45: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'o //
T02TD2736AE:123a-46: de nas thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis//
T02TD2736AE:123a-47: snod bcud sbyangs te sku la bsdu //
T02TD2736AE:123a-48: sku yang gsung yig rim gyis ni //
T02TD2736AE:123a-49: thig le mi dmigs gzugs su bsdu //
T02TD2736AE:123a-50: mtshan ma'i rtog pa rab zhi ba //
T02TD2736AE:123a-51: chos dbyings dag pa'i ngo bo nyid //
T02TD2736AE:123a-52: rang bzhin kun tu 'od gsal ba'i //
T02TD2736AE:123a-53: de bzhin nyid kyi dang du gzhag / de las cung zad lha yi skur //
T02TD2736AE:123b-0: @123b langs te spyod lam rnam bzhi ru //
T02TD2736AE:123b-1: ma yengs chu bo'i rgyun ltar bsgom //
T02TD2736AE:123b-2: snang grag sku gsung thugs su khyer //
T02TD2736AE:123b-3: gzhan yang bsod nams tshogs bsags phyir //
T02TD2736AE:123b-4: mdun gyi mandal dbus nyid du //
T02TD2736AE:123b-5: rten las dam tshig dkyil 'khor bskyed //
T02TD2736AE:123b-6: ye shes dkyil 'khor dbyings nas ni//
T02TD2736AE:123b-7: spyan drangs khrus gsol bstim bzhugs shing //
T02TD2736AE:123b-8: phyag 'tshal mchod cing bstod bya ste //
T02TD2736AE:123b-10: gsang sngags dmigs shing bzlas par bya //
T02TD2736AE:123b-11: de nas bzod gsol ye shes gshegs //
T02TD2736AE:123b-12: dam tshig dkyil 'khor rang la bsdu //
T02TD2736AE:123b-13: rang yang mi dmigs rgyas btab ste //
T02TD2736AE:123b-14: lha yi rnam par langs te gnas //
T02TD2736AE:123b-15: thun bzhi la sogs thun bar du //
T02TD2736AE:123b-16: chos kyi spyod pa rgya cher bya //
T02TD2736AE:123b-17: de las byung ba'i bsod nams kyang //
T02TD2736AE:123b-18: 'gro don byang chub chen por bsngo //
T02TD2736AE:123b-20: mtshan bzang mthong na don chen brnyes //
T02TD2736AE:123b-21: sum byed drug 'bum thon nas ni //
T02TD2736AE:123b-22: sna tshogs las kyi rim par sbyar //
T02TD2736AE:123b-23: lnga brgya'i tha mar 'jig rten du //
T02TD2736AE:123b-24: thub pa'i bstan pa rgyas 'gyur te /
T02TD2736AE:123b-27: thugs rje padmo rgyas pa'i ge sar las byung ba'i //
T02TD2736AE:123b-28: rgyas byed bcud ldan sbrang rtsi cung zad bdag gis 'thungs //
T02TD2736AE:123b-29: 'di ni gzhan phan bsam pas man ngag zur tsam bkod //
T02TD2736AE:123b-30: nyes gyur thugs rje'i dang du bzod pa mdzad par rigs //
T02TD2736AE:123b-31: 'dab chags rgyal pos chu las 'o ma blangs pa ltar //
T02TD2736AE:123b-32: grub pa'i rgyud las snying po 'di bsdus dge ba yis //
T02TD2736AE:123b-33: mu mtha' yas pa'i sems can ma lus thams cad kun //
T02TD2736AE:123b-34: rnam dag padmo'i zhing du rgyal ba'i zhal mthong shog / thugs rje chen po'i sgrub thabs yid bzhin nor bu zhes bya ba slob dpon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2736AE:123b-36: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po slob dpon padma'i zhal snga nas dang /
T02TD2736AE:123b-37: bod kyi lo ts'a ba btsun pa rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyis bsgyur ba'o//
